 to Github repo</small></li>\r\n	<li>Repeat</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Get going with Github', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '73-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-08-06 09:44:28', '2014-08-06 14:44:28', '', 73, 'http://dev.railsvitamins.com/73-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
